10:T49b,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"TVSeries","name":"Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World- Season 3","description":"The third season of <i>Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu</i>. <br><br>\n\nA year has passed since Subaru’s victory at the Sanctuary. He savors a life of fulfillment while Emilia’s camp stands united for the royal selection—until a fateful letter arrives. Anastasia, a royal selection candidate, has invited Emilia to the Watergate City of Priestella. But as the party begins its journey, crisis stirs beneath the surface and Subaru meets a cruel fate once again.<br><br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll) <br><br>\n\n<i>Note: The first episode has an extended runtime of ~90 minutes, and received an early premiere at Anime Expo on July 5, 2024.</i>","image":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx163134-yieRFbvUOH9a.jpg","datePublished":"2024-10-02","numberOfEpisodes":16,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","inLanguage":"ja","genre":["Action","Adventure","Drama","Fantasy","Psychological","Romance","Thriller"],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":8.4,"bestRating":10,"ratingCount":0}}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$10"}}],["$","$L11",null,{"initialDrama":{"id":"1e962591-593b-4e2f-b654-ba1154ed1b88","tmdb_id":163134,"imdb_id":null,"content_type":"anime","title":"Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World- Season 3","original_title":"Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 3rd season","overview":"The third season of <i>Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu</i>. <br><br>\n\nA year has passed since Subaru’s victory at the Sanctuary. He savors a life of fulfillment while Emilia’s camp stands united for the royal selection—until a fateful letter arrives. Anastasia, a royal selection candidate, has invited Emilia to the Watergate City of Priestella. But as the party begins its journey, crisis stirs beneath the surface and Subaru meets a cruel fate once again.<br><